{"tid":454267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港法律改革委員會前主席：中國削弱香港法治；英國袖手旁觀。","createTime":"2017-11-01T03:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T14:26:06.000Z","uid":47359,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3be5c555239d6ad469a4cc4599220d500c693046","tid":454267,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/10/prof-carol-jones-uk-unwilling-to-tackle-china-when-it-contravenes-joint-declaration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F10%2Fprof-carol-jones-uk-unwilling-to-tackle-china-when-it-contravenes-joint-declaration%2F&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d192a20a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/10/prof-carol-jones-uk-unwilling-to-tackle-china-when-it-contravenes-joint-declaration/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港法律改革委員會前主席：中國削弱香港法治；英國袖手旁觀。 Prof. Carol Jones: UK Unwilling to tackle China when it Contravenes Joint Declaration<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾焯文報導 (Chapman Chen reports)<br />\n<br />\n英國智庫亨利傑克遜學會（Henry Jackson Society）的亞洲研究中心今日（十月三十一日）發表論文報告：「香港二十年：公民、政治、法律權利的倒退」(Dr John Hemmings 及 Dr Malte Kaeding主編）。其中一位作者英國伯明翰法學教授嘉露&bull;鍾詩教授 (Prof. Carol Jones)，香港法律改革委員會前主席，認為九七前香港雖無政治權利，但有法律保障。九七後，由於中國干預，香港法治大為削弱。中方明明違反聯合聲明，英國卻袖手旁觀。(節錄）<br />\nHenry Jackson Society&rsquo;s report on the civil, political and legal rights of Hong Kong, twenty years after its handover to China, was published today. One of the authors of the report, Prof. Carol Jones, law professor from the University of Birmingham, former Chair, Hong Kong Law Reform Committee, concludes, &ldquo;Before 1997, Hongkongers were given legal rights rather than political rights&hellip; Since 1997, however, the rule of law has been weakened by poorly judged mainland interventions. The UK is apparently unwilling to tackle China when it fails to live up its commitments under the JD.&rdquo; Quoting Chen, Chapman, &ldquo;Down with Evil Ordinance, Uphold Human Rights, Set Free the Righteous!&rdquo; she states that clashes on 9 February 2016 prompted claims that the authorities contravened fair trial principles of presumption of innocence and proportionality of penalty Local Press, 17 October 2017 (節錄）<br />\n<br />\n九七後，中國及香港政府的舉動不時影響香港法治。中英聯合聲明明明係兩個主權國簽訂的國際條約，本年七月中國竟宣稱不再生效。<br />\n<br />\n近年警察濫權，政治檢控，日益增加。警察濫捕虐打示威人士，例如舊年二月旺角警民衝突，令人懷疑當局違反無罪推定及按公眾利益及罪行輕重判刑等公平審訊原則(鍾教授注明參考過曾焯文評論文章：Chen, C., &lsquo;Down with Evil Ordinance, Uphold Human Rights, Set Free the Righteous!&rsquo;, Local Press, 17 October 2017.)。此外，律政司在黃之鋒等社運人士受完非監禁懲罰後，再上訴呈請法庭重判其入獄，變相剝奪其參選權，其他佔中人士命運亦相同，令人懷疑律政司是否有政治動機。"},{"pid":"993a00f50ac4de75a65e6bb285872bec4ce18c4a","tid":454267,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘董建華引入釋法</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd62d1b618136775135eaabb6fe156583ad0b9cf","tid":454267,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n負擔到既捐下錢畀網媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73d4b70620c6a32bcdf6b0c2073752bc827d1e1","tid":454267,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話<br />\n負擔到既捐下錢畀網媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a264cc0a63e472bba1f3639746be188d2b152df","tid":454267,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>題外話<br />\n負擔到既捐下錢畀網媒